<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَنقص ككبر عبد<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فزادت قوته بِالْكبرِ ونقصت الرَّغْبَة فِيهِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
